column4: I was running apt-get dist-upgrade and it gave me an option to review the differences between the old modified file and the new maintained file. I got done reading the log but I don't know how to go back to the installation... I've got a blackened (END) at the prompt.
How do I get back to installation?
you are in less. press q.
less is a replacement for more (a pager, that lets you review the output of some long command)
